          <p class="lead">Senior Software Engineer with 8+ years of experience building production platforms across sports streaming, delivery, fintech, e-commerce, HR tech, transportation, and public-sector systems, specializing in microservices and CI/CD pipelines.</p>
          <div class="actions" aria-label="Profile links">
