            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Cloud Native</h3>
              <p>Containerized applications, Kubernetes, CI/CD, AWS, GCP, and deployment readiness.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Product Platforms</h3>
              <p>Full-stack product work across streaming, delivery, trading, e-commerce, and HR tech.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="experience" aria-labelledby="experience-title" data-reveal>
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Experience highlights</div>
              <h2 id="experience-title">Platforms, teams, and production systems.</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Most of my professional work has been developed in private repositories for production systems.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline">
            <article class="role">
              <time>Mar 2024 — Present</time>
              <h3>PlayOnSports / Nortal</h3>
